Exemplos comandos
   command youtube-dl
	youtube-dl -ciw -o '/home/wlainer/Videos/%(title)s.%(ext)s' -f 22/18/35/34 -a diversos

   extrair video
	ffmpeg -acodec copy -vcodec copy -ss 00:03:07 -t 00:09:22 -i ORIGINALFILE.mp4 OUTFILE-1.mp4


Things to do after install ubuntu

   * scroll bar overlay
	12.04	gsettings set org.gnome.desktop.interface ubuntu-overlay-scrollbars false
	14.04	gsettings set com.canonical.desktop.interface scrollbar-mode normal

   * turn off logon sound
	sudo gedit /usr/share/glib-2.0/schemas/50_unity-greeter.gschema.override
	copy into file
	   [com.canonical.unity-greeter]play-ready-sound = false

   * lock folder
	http://www.liberiangeek.net/2012/04/create-a-private-password-protected-folder-in-ubuntu-11-10-12-04/

   * Enable hibernate
	12.04:	sudo gedit /var/lib/polkit-1/localauthority/50-local.d/hibernate.pkla
		copy into file
		   [Re-enable Hibernate]
		   Identity=unix-user:*
		   Action=org.freedesktop.upower.hibernate
		   ResultActive=yes

	14.04: http://ubuntuhandbook.org/index.php/2014/04/enable-hibernate-ubuntu-14-04/

   * encrypt usb device
	http://www.liberiangeek.net/2012/04/encrypt-your-external-usb-drives-in-ubuntu-12-04-precise-pangolin/

   * disabel global menu
	sudo apt-get autoremove appmenu-gtk appmenu-gtk3 appmenu-qt

   * unsettings
	http://www.liberiangeek.net/2012/04/easily-configure-ubuntu-12-04-precise-pangolin-with-unsettings/

   * show data and time on the clock
	gsettings set com.canonical.indicator.datetime show-date true

   * backup whole computer
	http://www.liberiangeek.net/2012/07/backup-restore-your-whole-ubuntu-computer-using-remastersys/

   * bitdefender
	http://www.liberiangeek.net/2012/07/install-bitdefender-from-its-software-repository-in-ubuntu-12-04/

   * remove white dots
	sudo xhost +SI:localuser:lightdm
	sudo su lightdm -s /bin/bash
	gsettings set com.canonical.unity-greeter draw-grid false

   * gnome advanced settings
	sudo apt-get install gnome-tweak-tool

   * Ubuntu tweak
	sudo add-apt-repository ppa:tualatrix/ppa
	sudo apt-get update
	sudo apt-get install ubuntu-tweak

   * recent notifications
 	sudo add-apt-repository ppa:jconti/recent-notifications
	sudo apt-get update
	sudo apt-get install indicator-notifications

   * compression / decompress tools
	sudo apt-get install p7zip-rar p7zip-full unace unrar zip unzip sharutils rar uudeview mpack arj cabextract file-roller

   * backlight
	sudo apt-get install xbacklight
	startup command
	   xbacklight -set 15

   * autumount disk
	sudo apt-get install udisks
	startup command	
	   /usr/bin/udisks --mount /dev/disk/by-uuid/7E14FF8D14FF4725

   * configure notifications
	http://www.webupd8.org/2012/06/closable-movable-notifyosd.html

   * minimize on click
	http://itsfoss.com/enable-minimize-click-ubuntu-1404/

   * ambientes virtuais python
	http://hltbra.blogspot.com.br/2010/05/gerenciando-ambientes-virtuais-e.html

   * configurar joystick
	sudo apt-get install jstest-gtk
	http://hltbra.blogspot.com.br/2010/05/gerenciando-ambientes-virtuais-e.html

   * transparencia menus
	http://jwigley.com/2012/04/27/making-ubuntu-unity-look-beautiful-by-enabling-transparency/

   * nemo ubuntu 14.04
	http://www.webupd8.org/2013/10/install-nemo-with-unity-patches-and.html

   * quiterss
	sudo add-apt-repository ppa:quiterss/quiterss
	sudo apt-get update
	sudo apt-get install quiterss

   * integrate keepass firefox
	http://www.sysads.co.uk/2014/05/integrate-keepass-2-firefox-keefox-ubuntu-14-04-13-10/
